1. Project title

Hotel Reservation Cancellation Prediction

2. Short description

Machine learning project that predicts whether a hotel reservation will be canceled using booking data.

3. Dataset

119,590 hotel booking records.

4. Tools

Python, Pandas, NumPy, Scikit-learn, Matplotlib, Seaborn.

5. Workflow

Data cleaning

Missing value handling

Exploratory data analysis

Feature engineering

Model training

Model evaluation

6. Results

Model: Random Forest

F1-score: 76%

ROC-AUC: 84%

7. How to run

1. Clone the repository

2. Install requirements

3. Run the notebook
